│ my file editing issues, the solution is clear.                                                                                                                                                                 │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ The crash occurs because the SLP vectorizer tries to process terminator instructions (like `ret void`), which have no next instruction (`getNextNode()` returns null). This causes the assertion               │
│ `assert(ScheduleEnd && "tried to vectorize a terminator?")` to fail.                                                                                                                                           │
